creator: William Bell Scott
description:
LibriVox recording of End of Harvest by William Bell Scott.

Read in English by Chris Pyle; Greg Giordano; Ian King; Jason Mills; Julia Niedermaier; Leonard Wilson; MaryAnn; and Rosslyn Carlyle.

Librivox volunteers bring you eight readings of End of Harvest, by William Bell Scott. This is the fortnightly poetry project for November 9, 2014.

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
